desc: Selling paint and embellishments for the savvy DIYer, including Wise Owl Paint online, Iron Orchid Designs items in store and more, and I also paint custom furniture and make handmade rosaries and keepsakes using dried flowers from your significant life events such as a wedding or funeral.
